sentences.english: Kelli Kirk is a writer, baker, mom and human resources manager.
sentences.chinese: 凱利柯克是一位作家，麪包師，媽媽和人力資源經理。

sentences.english: Kelley, a critically acclaimed singer-songwriter, is due to release a new album in February.
sentences.chinese: 作爲創作型歌手的凱利將在明年二月發行新唱片。

sentences.english: There will be a "one screen for all, " Kelly says.
sentences.chinese: 凱利稱未來將會有張顯視屏包含了所有。

sentences.english: Karen Zhou is perhaps an exception.
Kelly swore quietly, looking at the deep cut on his left hand.
sentences.chinese: 凱利看着自己左手上深深的傷口，嘴裏暗罵了一句。

sentences.english: Spider kelly taught them to box like featherweights .
sentences.chinese: 斯拜德凱利教他們像次輕量級拳擊手那樣去打拳。

sentences.english: Dressed in his doctor's gown he went in to see her.
sentences.chinese: 身穿醫生大褂的凱利醫生來到病房看她。

sentences.english: He and his wife navigated their car around fallen trees and other debris to get to Kerri's home.
sentences.chinese: 他和妻子開車繞過倒下的樹和其他雜物來到凱利的家。

sentences.english: Kelly requested the business office to pass the final bill to him for approval.
sentences.chinese: 凱利醫生請求財務室把醫療賬單寄給他。

sentences.english: Ellen Kelly, budding with womanhood and childfresh happiness.
sentences.chinese: 埃倫凱利，處於女子花樣年華，又帶着孩子般的喜悅。

sentences.english: Kevin Kelly once explained how to calculate the date of your death.
sentences.chinese: 凱文凱利曾經解釋過如何計算死亡的日期。

sentences.english: Kelly Yang is a Chinese girl .
sentences.chinese: 楊凱利是一箇中國女孩。

sentences.english: Kelly said all the painters got along.
sentences.chinese: 凱利說，所有參展畫家均友好相處。

sentences.english: In August, Delaney steamed out there with co-chief scientist Debbie Kelley.
sentences.chinese: 在8月，德萊尼蒸出與合作的首席科學家黛比凱利。

sentences.english: Kelley has a history of groundbreaking teaching methods.
sentences.chinese: 過去凱利曾經嘗試過開創性的教學方法。

sentences.english: His parents anticipate Garys return home will be soon.
sentences.chinese: 凱利的雙親認爲他不久就會回家。
